run intellij dokcer
1. install plugin bashSUpport
file > setting > plugin > bashSUpport

2. run/debug configuration:
 pilih bash > add(+) > 
   a. restart spring
      script :  docker-compose restart spring
      interpreter path : /bin/bash
      interpreter options : -c
   
   b. compile spring
      script :  docker-compose up --force-recreate spring
      interpreter path : /bin/bash
      interpreter options : -c  
      
   c. logs spring
      script :  docker-compose logs -f spring
      interpreter path : /bin/bash
      interpreter options : -c  
      
     
